    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in as-is condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows extensive wear, including several large dents, noticeable rust spots on the wheel arches, and a heavily faded paint job. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a persistent oil leak and a loud exhaust, while the transmission shifts roughly between gears. The interior has seen better days, with visible tears in the upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and non-functioning air conditioning. This would be an ideal project car or a source for parts for someone with the right tools and time.",
