      "description": "Hey there! I'm finally parting with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this beauty is in such incredible shape, you'd think it just rolled off the showroom floor today! It\u2019s been meticulously cared for and looks absolutely stunning inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect and ready for a new home, this is the one for you. Come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
